      "rationale": "CFD-predicted RHI values were compared against published experimental RHI measurements from a geometrically similar centrifugal pump platform. Mean signed error was +0.04 RHI units (4.3% relative) across the five operating points. The comparison is considered adequate for MRL 2 worst-case rank-ordering. The positive bias is conservative for the acceptance criterion RH < 1."
